<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.2">
<l>nīlat taṭavarai māmaṇi nikaḻak kiṭantatupō laravaṇai</l>
<l>vēlait talaikkiṭan tāyaṭiyēṉ maṉattiruntāy</l>
<l>cōlait talaikkaṇa māmayil naṭamāṭa maḻaimukil pōṉṟeḻun teṅkum</l>
<l>ālaip pukaikamaḻu maṇiyāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You [once] lay in the ocean on a serpent bed, like a great sapphire lying</l>
<l rend="indent">as it shines on a wide blue mountain;</l>
<l>[Now] you are in the mind of [your] servant, me,</l>
<l>Lord of lovely Āli scented by steam from [boiling] sugarcane juice,</l>
<l rend="indent">rising everywhere like monsoon rainclouds,</l>
<l>So that great flocks of peacocks in the garden perform a dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
